Hello All,
Following on from my email below =E2=80=93 I am confirming the following si=
te visits where I will meet onsite with contractors to commence the process=
 of obtaining repair proposals:

  *   Arc Projects =E2=80=93 16/12/2025 =E2=80=93 3:00pm
  *   Asset Managers =E2=80=93 17/12/2025 =E2=80=93 12:30pm
  *   JLG =E2=80=93 16/12/2025 =E2=80=93 1:30pm
Further updates to follow.
Regards,
Grant.

