k-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello All,<o:p></o:=
p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Following on from m=
y email below =E2=80=93 I am confirming the following site visits where I w=
ill meet onsite with contractors to commence the process of obtaining repai=
r proposals:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo13"><span sty=
le=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Arc Projects =E2=80=93 16/12/2025 =E2=80=93 3:00pm<=
o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 l=
evel1 lfo13"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Asset Managers =E2=80=93 17/1=
2/2025 =E2=80=93 12:30pm<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagrap=
h" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo13"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">JLG =
=E2=80=93 16/12/2025 =E2=80=93 1:30pm<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Further updates to =
follow.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regards,<o:p></o:p>=
</span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. <o:p></o:p><=
/span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
