<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-line-height-alt:.75pt"><span style=3D"f=
ont-size:1.0pt;color:white">Good afternoon Grant, Thanks for your email bel=
ow. My client does not accept that this scope includes all the necessary wo=
rk to reinstate the fire damage at her
 house. However, in order to keep this claim moving towards resolution, ple=
ase proceed<o:p></o:p></span></p>
