<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-=
family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">Lance, we are waiting for your assessm=
ent of temporary accommodation costs. We discussed whether an additional su=
m could be paid on the basis that there was delay
 in commissioning testing. Raffaella is now out of pocket for temporary acc=
ommodation so your response on this point would be appreciated.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
